Cline / Roo Cline: Before touching anything in this repository, read
AGENTS.md at the repo root.

It documents:
- The exact Docker service name (`algo`) and compose binary
  (`docker-compose`, hyphenated V1)
- When `--no-cache` is and isn't appropriate
- Tick-rounding invariants (must use `core.family.round_price_to_tick`)
- Maker-only invariants on `chase_buy`/`chase_sell`
- The hardcoded session schedule and reporting cadence
- Things prior agent sessions got wrong — DO NOT REPEAT them

AGENTS.md is the single source of truth.
